2, \"to\": 2329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As part of the preparations for the Olympics, French authorities evicted them and removed all their belongings.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7423539906441782, \"rank\": 0.32509099506935796, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"the preparations\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2402}, {\"ngram\": \"all their belongings\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of the tents, there are large LEGO-like blocs of concrete with spikes on top of them to ensure that no one can sleep there.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tents\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"large LEGO-like blocs\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"concrete\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"spikes\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an operation that has been repeated again and again across encampments in Paris, targeting up to 12,500 families living in shelters, migrants, homeless and sex workers.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2686, \"end\": 2691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.755458682835389e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an operation\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"encampments\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 12,500 families\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"shelters\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"migrants\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2753}, {\"ngram\": \"homeless and sex workers\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was all part of Macron's plan to showcase France's grandeur during the Games.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2801, \"end\": 2807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.806794681535754e-32, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999994561222, \"rank\": 3.171187601916261e-10, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people were relocated to temporary accommodation in Paris, others were put on buses and driven to cities like Marseille and Lyon, as there are not enough shelters in the capital.\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 3047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2921, \"end\": 2926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.755458682835389e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2979, \"end\": 2988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5530896889624925e-17, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso