d\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huot_Automatic_Rifle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huot_Automatic_Rifle\"}, {\"begin\": 3196, \"end\": 3201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.755458682835389e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3202, \"end\": 3212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solidarity\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.807491594582669e-16, \"text\": \"Solidarity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solidarity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solidarity\"}, {\"begin\": 3265, \"end\": 3271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7423539906441782, \"rank\": 0.32509099506935796, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lawyer\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro.co.uk\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3234}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few months\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"social cleansing\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It concerns all people who live and work in the streets, who it does not want tourists to see - migrants, homeless, drug users and even sex workers.\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all people\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3352}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3385}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3416}, {\"ngram\": \"- migrants\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3434}, {\"ngram\": \"homeless, drug users\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3456}, {\"ngram\": \"even sex workers\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are just pushed away instead of being taken care of.\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are not against the Olympics; we share a lot of values like solidarity and friendship between people from different countries.\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3586}, {\"ngram\": \"values\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3596}, {\"ngram\": \"solidarity\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3612}, {\"ngram\": \"friendship\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3627}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3642}, {\"ngram\": \"different countries\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But if 1% of the budget for the Olympics had been dedicated to social issues, we could have offered proper housing to people.\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1%\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3680}, {\"ngram\": \"the budget\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3694}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3711}, {\"ngram\": \"social issues\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3747}, {\"ngram\": \"proper housing\", \"from\": 3771, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If a small budget was dedicated to this, we could have offered an actual dignified solution.\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small budget\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"an actual dignified solution\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Right now, we do not know what has happened to these people.\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these people\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are not to be seen anywhere.\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This has a very dangerous impact as many have health issues, which are not being taken care of.'\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 4083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very dangerous impact\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4019}, {\"ngram\": \"health issues\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4046}, {\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Place de la R\\u00e9publique in central Paris, a popular square for protests, activists gathered to show their solidarity with the victims and to shame authorities for 'playing ping pong' with their lives.\", \"from\": 4085, \"to\": 4287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4088, \"end\": 4110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_R\\u00e9publique\", \"score\": 0.9919463876317131, \"rank\": 0.007170795306387261, \"text\": \"Place de la R\\u00e9publique\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_R\\u00e9publique\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_R\\u00e9publique\"}, {\"begin\": 4122, \"end\": 4127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.755458682835389e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"protests\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4158}, {\"ngram\": \"activists\", \"from\": 4160, \"to\": 4169}, {\"ngram\": \"their solidarity\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4203}, {\"ngram\": \"the victims\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4220}, {\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4245}, {\"ngram\": \"ping pong\", \"from\": 4259, \"to\": 4268}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 4275, \"to\": 4286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several human rights groups were there for what they called 'Counter Opening Ceremony', giving speeches about the cost of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several human rights groups\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4316}, {\"ngram\": \"'Counter Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4374}, {\"ngram\": \"speeches\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4392}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 4399, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Various signs were dotted around the square.\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4470, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Various signs\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4439}, {\"ngram\": \"the square\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the bottom of the monument, a giant banner was draped, reading 'Jo de l'exclusion, 12,500 personnes \\u00e9xpuls\\u00e9es', translated to 'The Games of Exclusion, 12,500 evicted'.\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4538, \"end\": 4540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\", \"score\": 0.9666290607783639, \"rank\": 0.03442493835667735, \"text\": \"Jo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 4474, \"to\": 4484}, {\"ngram\": \"the monument\", \"from\": 4488, \"to\": 4500}, {\"ngram\": \"a giant banner\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"The Games\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4610}, {\"ngram\": \"Exclusion\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nathan Lequeux, an organiser for the activist group Utopia 56, said: 'They want to clean the city for the Olympic Games, for the tourists.\", \"from\": 4643, \"to\": 4781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4643, \"end\": 4649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\", \"score\": 0.9999371284767963, \"rank\": 6.287294727167374e-05, \"text\": \"Nathan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an organiser\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"the activist group\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4694}, {\"ngram\": \"Utopia\", \"from\": 4695, \"to\": 4701}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 4732, \"to\": 4740}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4762}, {\"ngram\": \"the tourists\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'As treatment of migrants is becoming more horrible and infamous, people are being chased off the streets.\", \"from\": 4783, \"to\": 4889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"treatment\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4796}, {\"ngram\": \"migrants\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4808}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4855}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 4877, \"to\": 4888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Since the Olympics, this aggressiveness, this policy of hunting has become more pronounced.'\", \"from\": 4891, \"to\": 4984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4898, \"to\": 4910}, {\"ngram\": \"this policy\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 4944}, {\"ngram\": \"hunting\", \"from\": 4948, \"to\": 4955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A report released in June by the collective Le Revers de la M\\u00e9daille, which represents 90 associations concluded that the \\u00cele-de-France region has been emptied of some of the people that 'the powers that be consider undesirable'.\", \"from\": 4986, \"to\": 5215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5033, \"end\": 5039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Revers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A report\", \"from\": 4986, \"to\": 4994}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5011}, {\"ngram\": \"90 associations\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5088}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00cele-de-France region\", \"from\": 5104, \"to\": 5128}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 5157, \"to\": 5167}, {\"ngram\": \"the powers\", \"from\": 5174, \"to\": 5184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christophe No\\u00ebl Du Payrat, chief of staff of the regional government, has firmly denied those accusations.\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5233, \"end\": 5235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Du_Li\", \"score\": 0.9727743487833256, \"rank\": 0.027942410173378767, \"text\": \"Du\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Du_Li\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Du_Li\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"chief\", \"from\": 5244, \"to\": 5249}, {\"ngram\": \"staff\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5258}, {\"ngram\": \"the regional government\", \"from\": 5262, \"to\": 5285}, {\"ngram\": \"those accusations\", \"from\": 5305, \"to\": 5322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He insisted that the government has relocated migrants from the city for years.\", \"from\": 5325, \"to\": 5404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 5342, \"to\": 5356}, {\"ngram\": \"migrants\", \"from\": 5371, \"to\": 5379}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 5385, \"to\": 5393}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 5398, \"to\": 5403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are taking care of them,' he said.\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 5444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 5421, \"to\": 5425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We do not really understand the criticism because we are very much determined to offer places for these people.'\", \"from\": 5445, \"to\": 5558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the criticism\", \"from\": 5474, \"to\": 5487}, {\"ngram\": \"places\", \"from\": 5533, \"to\": 5539}, {\"ngram\": \"these people\", \"from\": 5544, \"to\": 5556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get in touch with our news team by emailing us atwebnews@metro.co.uk.\", \"from\": 5560, \"to\": 5629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5617, \"end\": 5628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_n